			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
				I was born and brought up in a small village near Thrissur called Kolazhy in Kerala, India.
			</p>
			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
				My early passion for technology led me to pursue a unique course of study after the 7th
				grade. I joined Junior Technical High School, where I learned the basics of carpentry,
				mechanics, and electronics. After completing my 10th grade, my interest shifted towards
				embedded systems and programming, leading me to enroll in a Polytechnic program where I
				obtained my Computer Science Diploma. Following that, I pursued a B.Tech in Computer Science
